reviewText: If you love poetry, rage, dream, passion, exigency and romantism ; if you think that beauty can be an ideal and cinema can be new ; you will love "Docteur Chance", a jewel of cinematic poetry.

I love this film. It's so great... Es el WITKACY Movie...
ES EL CRAVAN MOVIE. ES EL RIGAUD MOVIE... All the heroes of this lost century are HERE...
Last message of an erotoman, toxicoman, megalomaniac...
